import { Modal, Button, Form } from "react-bootstrap";

function AddDepartmentPopUp(props) {
  console.log("hello");
  return (
    <Modal show={props.show} backdrop="static" keyboard={false}>
       <Form >
      <Modal.Header closeButton>
        <Modal.Title>Add New Department</Modal.Title>
      </Modal.Header>
      <Modal.Body>
       
          <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicDepartmentID">
            <Form.Label>Department ID</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control type="number" placeholder="Department ID" />
          </Form.Group>

          <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicDepartmetName">
            <Form.Label>Department Name</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Department Name" />
          </Form.Group>
      
      </Modal.Body>
      <Modal.Footer>
        <Button variant="secondary" onClick={props.hide}>
          Close
        </Button>
        <Button variant="primary" >
          Submit
        </Button>
      </Modal.Footer>
      </Form>
    </Modal>
  );
}

export default AddDepartmentPopUp;
